msgctxt "0001"
msgid "Not at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Absolutely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Sometimes during a class trial, your opponent simply\n"
"won't want to hear what you have to say.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>When this happens, you will engage them in\n"
"a head-to-head battle.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>We like to refer to this as the <CLT><CLT 3>Bullet Time Battle<CLT><CLT 23>\n"
"(AKA the BTB, BTW).\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>During the BTB, you want to <CLT><CLT 3>destroy<CLT><CLT 23> your <CLT><CLT 3>opponent's\n"
"statements<CLT><CLT 23> in time with the rhythm.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Match your <CLT><CLT 3>button presses<CLT><CLT 23> with each <CLT><CLT 3>Tempo Marker<CLT><CLT 23> as\n"
"they move across the screen and reach the center.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>…\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Press the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_LOCK_ON%<CLT><CLT 23> to <CLT><CLT 3>lock on<CLT><CLT 23> to an\n"
"opponent's statement.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Destroy the statement you've locked on to with the\n"
"<CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_ATTACK%<CLT><CLT 23> as the <CLT><CLT 3>Tempo Marker<CLT><CLT 23> reaches the center.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>…\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Use this method to <CLT><CLT 3>deal damage<CLT><CLT 23> to your opponent. If\n"
"you can't pull it off...you'll be the one in pain.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Do this consecutively and you'll start a <CLT><CLT 3>combo<CLT><CLT 23>. Keep\n"
"this going and you'll initiate a <CLT><CLT 3>Tempo Up<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>On the flipside, if you keep <CLT><CLT 3>missing<CLT><CLT 23>, you'll get\n"
"into a <CLT><CLT 3>Tempo Down<CLT><CLT 23> situation.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>When the tempo changes, so does the timing for\n"
"hitting each button.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>So watch out for that!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Deal enough damage to your opponent, and their <CLT><CLT 3>weak\n"
"spot statement<CLT><CLT 23> will appear.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>At that point, you can press the <CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_BULLET_TIME_ATTACK%<CLT><CLT 23> to shoot\n"
"it down with a <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Bullet<CLT><CLT 23>, like any other statement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Refute their statement fast enough, and you'll come\n"
"out <CLT><CLT 3>victorious<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>But just like before, if your Influence Gauge reaches\n"
"zero or you run out of time, <CLT><CLT 3>you fail<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Well then...good luck, and have fun!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your first <CLT><CLT 3>Bullet Time Battle<CLT><CLT 23> is about to begin.\n"
"Would you like to hear more?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
